
> JIRA CLOUD SUBSCRIPTION TIERS 
-- There are different subscription levels of Cloud. 
   a> FREE -> It allows upto 10 users. 
              But, no project permissions.
              Limited Automations. 
              2GB Storage space.
              No support from Atlassian, just the community support will be available. 

   b> STANDARD -> Higher Automation limit .
                  250GB Storage Space. 
                  It wiill allow standard functionality. 
                  They will provide 9/5 regional support. 

   c> PREMIUM -> It has unlimites storage.
                 It will offer unlimited automations. 
                 It will offer premium support. 
                 99.9% uptime SLA.
                 It will also offer AI support, Alassian Intelligence. 
                 Additional features includes plans, Archiving Insights, Sandbox etc. 

   d> ENTERPRISE -> It will everything from premium plus many more.
                    upto 150 jira instances. 
                    99.95% uptime. 
                    It will offer 24/7 support.
                    It will also offer Atlassian Guard , user management etc. 

   
